&gt; The x coordinate of the last touch on touch screen devices and the current mouse position on desktop for the first pointer **in screen coordinates**. The screen origin is the top left corner.

Since you want the **world coordinates** instead of the **screen coordinates** you need to [unproject](https://libgdx.badlogicgames.com/ci/nightlies/docs/api/com/badlogic/gdx/graphics/Camera.html#unproject-com.badlogic.gdx.math.Vector3-) the position of the mouse on the screen according to the camera:

